#### Secret that didn’t go in the pointers above-&nbsp;

It’s cheap. Your money sticks to your pocket.

It’s easy to use. No rocket science to sit and scratch your head all day.&nbsp;

It's customizable. Fill it, edit it, share it, save it, fill it, edit it and so on..

It’s flexible. Keep it in your computer at the office desk or carry it in your phone to the mountains as per your convenience.&nbsp;

> Not convinced? Say no to the excel sheets and kick the butts of your loyal employees
